For example, it says that Evasive allows a warrior to take less damage and that Defensive is pretty much just an upgrade.  <br>
<br>
This really isn't a very good description of what these discs do.  Evasive allows you to EVADE more hits, but also makes it so you are able to hit the mob less often.  The damage for all hits remains the same.  Defensive lets you get hit for less damage and also makes it so you hit for less damage.<br>
<br>
